On 12 Jun 2001, at 18:50, robertdahl wrote:

> The council member nodded, "Yes, now should be a good time to be
> prepared. A spy has informed me the Autobots are near leaving."
> ______________________________________________________________________
> In a bar Slugslinger was nursing a cup of oil. He smiled, and
> continued his speech, telling a robot beside him, of great victories
> in the path. "Well, the Autobots never could look at me straight after
> that." He said smilling. 
> 
> "Fascinating." The robot said in raspy tone, with kid like enthusiasm.
> "Ever since the Decepticons began, I wanted to join, but was never
> able to do good enough at the Decepticon battle academy." He turned
> his head to the robot beside him. "Although I am suprised my brother
> never made it." The robot just quietly downed his murky drink, and
> with red eyes looked at the other two.
